    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. the last ten years... all those papers, the grants, the theories... it was all just a house of cards. i was building on nothing. i feel like such a fraud, like i've just been playing a part in a play that's finally ended. there's nothing left for me now.",
